A few months ago, we were running this successful project with over 1700% achievement within 30 days. Thanks to our Kickstarter Angels, our project folded up with great applauses. It was fantastic experience and unforgettable! But we never ended up there though. We have been constantly receiving messages from a lot of people showing their interests in qualMeter series, thus, we decided to re launch qualMeter series as Pre-Sale project on Indiegogo In-Demand to serve more of our fans! QooPow™ qualMeter in the News: http://www.geeky-gadgets.com/qoometer-smart-usb-charger-hits-kickstarter-10-02-2016/ http://www.kicktraq.com/projects/1187836018/qoometer-finally-a-smart-usb-cable-charger-tester/ http://www.trendhunter.com/trends/charger-tester http://www.omicrono.com/2016/02/protege-tus-dispositivos-de-cables-usb-baratos-con-este-aparato/ (Spanish) http://www.shenzhenware.com/articles/10614 (Chinese-中文) http://www.eefocus.com/test-measurement/358677/r0 (Chinese-中文)  Introducing the QooPow™ qualMeter series  
 


QooPow™ qualMeter series are revolutionary, smart and cost-efficient DIY devices, which can simply help you to diagnostic and get to know the quality of your USB cables and chargers in a glance without any technical background. 
With a qualMeter product around, you will never need to worry about on getting wrong cables and chargers for your precious smartphone or tablet.
qualMeter series handle wide range of mainstream USB charging cables. It also tests loading capability of the 5v chargers to roughly define their quality.
 

  Why We Make qualMeter products?Our motivation for creating the QooPow™ qualMeter was from the observation that there are too many low quality and compromised charging products in the market, especially 3rd-party charging cables and chargers. There is lacking of an easy and simple way to measure the quality of charging cables and chargers for people.In our daily life, USB cables and chargers are playing big role of mobile device charging, therefore their quality is critical for the charging. Low quality charging cables and chargers could cause serious damage on your mobile devices or might even burn down your house. You can easily find tons of images, videos and stories by simply search Google and YouTube with keywords like charging cable burning, charger on fire etc. Well, a burning or something on fire is very obvious to us to catch. The question is how can we find it out before it burns? or even before we buy it?Furthermore, there are also other important but hidden impacts that most of people wouldn’t know in a easy way such as slow charging, strange behaviors on smart phone when charging, dropping data transfer and so on. The following Tip would give you some ideas about how a low quality charging cable will cause slow charging.Tech Tips:Wondering why is your charging so slow? A non-qualified charging cable could have a dramatic voltage drop. For example, if your charging cable's impedance is 500mΩ, which many low quality cables do. It will have 0.5v drop @1A charging current, that means you will only get 4.5v at the phone end when your charger provides 5v for charging. Most of smart phones won't even charge in this case. That explains a lot of charging issues we have.A Low Quality Cable at ChargingIn addition, the charging current is now getting higher and higher due to massive application of smart devices. Many devices are charged at 2A or above such as pads and tablets etc. The quality of charging cable has become critical nowadays. Take the given example above, it will have 1v dropping if you are charging at 2A current which leads to only 4v to the device end. Beside the safety issue you may have, there will be certainly no charging at this low voltage for smart devices.FYI, Check out this USB charging cable review video from YouTube: （in case if you are not able to watch here, here is the link: https://youtu.be/doMHmGatyYc）Unfortunately, like the above video, to evaluate the performance of the charging cable and charger is not really an easy task for most of non-tech people or even sometimes for tech people. It requires not only some electronic knowledge but also needs expensive testing equipment. People find it's very hard to deal with all different kind of massive charging products. QualMeter is the easiest and smart way for you to rule the charging.QooPow™ qualMeter series was initially made for our own lab demanding as we are developing smart and fast charging products for mobile devices. The purpose of making such tool was based on the situation that we needed to roughly measure the different qualities of the cables/chargers and their impact on our products’ performance. With qualMeter series, we are able to easily category the pile of cables and chargers without complicated reading and analyzing. When some of our friends were showing their great interests in this little device, we started to realize that it could benefit others. That's why we decided to take it to Indiegogo In-Demand project and to share with you.One of our friends, Rebecca, was suspecting on one of her new bought charging cables, which always felt hot when charging. We gave Rebecca one of our qualMeter prototypes for testing. By using the qualMeter, she was able to find out this cable was in a bad condition before the wire burns on fire. She then checked rest of her cables and chargers, and was able to eliminate 2 other bad cables and 1 bad charger. The next day, Rebecca went shopping. With a little help from qualMeter she bought 3 good cables in a decent price. The businessman was shocked to see her using qualMeter and even asked her where to get one. Lol~ Rebecca was extremely happy with qualMeter, because she's smarter. What makes the qualMeter so unique is that it comes along with a simple idea that everyone can measure the quality of random cable/charger in a simple way, an affordable way. It intends to provide an easy and simple solution in a fairly low cost. qualMeter series is designed for non-tech people but can certainly be used by tech-savvies for roughly testing as well. Who would need QooPow™ qualMeter series?If you…
Are unsure about the quality of your USB cable & charger;
Are looking for safe and faster charging; 
Don’t want to be cheated by those unscrupulous businessmen; 
Are tired with poor quality of charging cables and chargers; 
Have ever been in dilemma of choosing right USB cable/charger; 
Are dealing with USB cables/chargers as a business; 
Wanted to have easier and simpler solution to rank the pile of cables/chargers; 
More... The Features of QooPow™ qualMeter seriesDespite that versions vary slightly based on their functionalities, qualMeter is basically made for testing USB charging cables and chargers. It has two major functions:Cable Test Mode - Simply connect both ends of your USB charging cable with qualMeter and plug it into any 5v USB charging port. You can read the LED indicators to have an idea about the quality of your charging cable.Charger Test Mode - Simply plug qualMeter into any 5v USB charging port. You can read the LED indicators to have an idea about the quality of your USB Charger.QualMeter has embedded an ultra low power Micro-Processor, a brain, to provide the ability of being smart. Beside its main Cable Test and Charger Test features, it also comes with the following highlighted features:Cable Shielded Test – A shielded cable usually has better quality. It’s not only good for charging but also a benefit for data transferring.Cable Short Circuit Test - When you plug qualMeter at Cable Test Mode, the red LED indicator will start flashing If your cable is shorted. You should stop using this cable immediately!Reversible USB plug – With the reversible USB plug design, you don’t have to worried about the direction of plugging into a USB charging port.    Plug n Play – qualMeter comes with no switch or any control button. There is no manual operation needed to be done. It works automatically according to the status it detects. How does QooPow™ qualMeter work?qualMeter is designed to provide a simple and straightforward way to test cable and charger without any technical background. That means with qualMeter in hand, everyone is able to distinguish the quality of a cable or a charger.Simply connect the cable you want to test into corresponding ports as following diagramQooPow™ qualMeter has two main testing modes, cable test and charger test. It automatically switches between two modes. Charger Test Mode: Without cable plugged in, Charger test mode is enabled right away when qualMeter has been plugged into an USB power source. The orange charger test indicator lights up and it also confirms the testing current is 1A. You can find out the quality of this charger at 1A output by reading the Quality Indicators on the left. Cable Test Mode: Cable test mode will be enabled when both ends of a cable have been connected with qualMeter. Then plug qualMeter into an USB power source. The blue cable test indicator (the left one) will be turned on. You can find out the quality of this cable by reading the Quality Indicators on the left.  Shielded Indication: At the Cable Test mode, if the blue Shielded Indicator (the right one) lights up, it means this cable is shielded.  Cable Short Circuit Test - is as simple as other functions. Just plug both ends of the cable into qualMeter as usual, then plug qualMeter into any 5v USB port. The red LED indicator will start flashing If your cable is shorted. Otherwise, if the cable is not shorted, the qualMeter will automatically start the Cable Test mode to tell you how good is this cable. That’s it ! :)   How to read the testing results? Unlike regular testing devices, there are no numbers bother to read, no buttons, no extra operations, no calculations and no technical background are needed. All you need to know is just colors, the Green, Yellow and Red, which correspond to Good, Fair(OK) and Bad. That’s it! You see colors; you see the quality of your cable and charger. QooPow™ qualMeter is suitable for wide range of mainstream cables and is compatible with most of major 5v USB chargers.Specifications 

Main Material：Raw PCB (CCL FR-4) Pb free

Dimension: 47.8mm x 23.8mm x 11mm (the length of the USB plug is not included)

Power Input: USB Type A reversible Male Connector

Input Voltage: 4.5~5.5v

Cable Test Connectors: USB Type A Female Connector, 4 types of mainstream charging connectors such as Micro-USB, Mini-USB and others.

Charger Test Current: @1A

LED Indicators: Green x2, Yellow x2, Red x2, Blue x2 and Orange x1  
  The more advanced version - qualMeter X In response to many requests from our angel backers of our previous campaign, we brought up qualMeter X version into our QooPow™ qualMeter product series. It comes with more advanced features than basic version.  It provides more advanced Charger Test function by allowing 1A/1.5A/2A/2.5A/3A output testing and an Output Compensation indicator, which can cover almost all major USB chargers  Here are the list of the functions on qualMeter X: 
All functions from qualMeter basic version; 
2x USB Type-C ports are now added (which you are all asking for :)); 
Advanced Cable Test Mode, @1A/2A; 
Advanced Charger Test Mode, Full range 1~3.1A (100mA step) Current testing; 
Adjustable Electronic Load;
Output Compensation Indication;
32-bit 48MHz MCU;
Flash memory for saving the last testing result;
Specially made transparent enclosure;
Extension for Future Functions.
 The qualMeter X is about 1/3 bigger compare to qualMeter basic version.  More information please visit our website www.qoopow.comHow does qualMeter X work?Same as qualMeter basic, the X version is also simple to use.   The Enclosure for qualMeter X As we have promised during Kickstarter Campaign, a transparent enclosure has been designed and will be shipped together with qualMeter X. As the result, The original idea of RAW-PCBA looking qualMeter X is no longer available. However, since the enclosure is still in the molding stage we don't have the real product picture yet. It will be updated as soon as we have the final product in hand. Accessory for qualMeter - miniLoad    miniLoad is the complement to qualMeter basic version providing wider range of charger testing functionality. Due to the infrastructure of qualMeter, it's not possible to directly add the charger testing load on the mainboard since we also wanted to keep the simplicity of the qualMeter.QooPow miniLoad is specially designed to extend charger testing range for qualMeter basic version. It provides the ability to allow qualMeter basic tests 2.1/2.4/3A output of the charger. Simply use the switch to switch among 2.1A, 2.4A and 3A.  MiniLoad is very simple to use. When inserted the rear socket of qualMeter basic version, it connects as extension.QualMeter basic version with miniLoad is not duplicate to X version. Different from qualMeter X, the combination of the "qualMeter basic & miniLoad" is aiming to simple and rough testing for non-tech people. It only has 4 stops 1A, 2.1A, 2.4A and 3A for most of the common chargers in the market. While qualMeter X can measure more detailed current output from 1A to 3.1A with 100mA each step.Notice: miniLoad can only work with qualMeter basic version. It doesn't work as an individual load, neither work for qualMeter X.  The Perks Currently, we only offer qualMeter X version due to the strategic adjustment on our products line. The perks with qualMeter Basic version are not available any more.Note: All pre-ordered qualMeter X will be shipped with an enclosure. The Schedule for Pre Order DeliveryFor Indiegogo InDemand Pre-Sale project, the nearest delivery time will be on May 2017.Notice: This schedule is subjected to change. It may delay if our pre-sale order doesn't meet the manufactures' minimum order requirement. Or it may be pre-dated if we can meet the manufactures' minimum order requirement earlier.If you don't want to wait and wanted to get the qualMeters as soon as possible, you can visit our online store and get qualMeters at regular retail price.  We reserve small amount of inventory for web sale after our first mass production. Who we are Intelliplus is a creative tech start-up formed in 2013, who is focusing on Smart-Ware development. Our vision is to Make Life Easier & Simpler. Currently our main development team is based in Chengdu, China. Chengdu is one of the biggest cities in western china. With her over 2,500 years of historical and humanistic culture, Chengdu is also well known as the cradle of China IT industry. And our manufacturing partners are mainly located in Shenzhen, China, where is the world's IT manufacturing center. We have been contracting and working with one of the top Internet Companies in China and helping them to build fast charging products under their own brand since 2014. By going deeper and gaining more knowledge on the fast charging technologies, we think it’s time to launch our own smart charging products and brand - The QooPow™ series. On our mind, charging is one of the things that should be peaceful and joyful like art. It should be a part of our quality life. Despite there are plenty of charging related products in the market, few of them can stand out. In fact, there are too many low quality and compromised products. People deserve better charging products! We believe we can do better! And here we go. By launching the QooPow™ qualMeter as pre-sale project with the excitement, we are proud that we have made it and will continue to do so. Other QooPow™ series smart charging products are in the line of development, more to come. The core team  What you can help us?  Our efforts over the past two years on smart and fast charging technologies have helped to bring qualMeter series onto Indiegogo In-Demand stage where you are connected to participate. A journey we have started to Make Life Easier and Simpler, and to free our mind to make our world a better place!  qualMeter series is our ice breaker to the world. And now, we are heading to mass production and turn our idea into real market!  Thank you! qualMeter lovers and Viewers, with your help and support we can:  
Purchase all materials for production;
Build up global Distribution; 
Setup customer service team;
Continue to develop, to optimize and to upgrade products;
Increase our unit shipment;
Make us stronger;
