  Big thank you & Stay in touch!Big thank you to everyone who stops by here. Our team is fully committed to support not only our backers, buyers but all our community.  Register on our QooPow™ Smart & Fast Charging forum and subscribe to our Newsletter in receiving the rewards, exclusive offer for backers, specials, discounts and latest news updates and in answering all the issues and concerns in time! Below are more ways to stay connected with us. Please join us and be part of our happy journey!  https://www.facebook.com/qoopower/ https://twitter.com/qoopowhttps://plus.google.com/107882179424471324735Risks and challenges Mass Production:Production is jumping on the stage at the moment as we are rolling the schedule down towards fruition. We have fully understanding that production plays big role in the project and also we are also aware that there might always be some unforeseen troubles in the way to mass production. We will further leverage our resources and try all the angles to ensure our expectations are met. Our manufacturing partners we’ve been working with are the tops in the industry with decades of experiences. We have locked down high quality and schedule with agreement to ensure the orders are fulfilled as promised.Product updates:As all our community know that most of pictures showing above are not final version. The product details may be slightly different over the manufacturing process. Optimization is what it takes and more to lock off highest quality possible. The updates will be regularly sent out to our community.Delivery:Since all the manufacturing will be done in China, the rewards will be sent from China as well. We are aware that there may be issues that are unexpected when it comes to international shipping. Our solution is to set up second backup in logistics to avoid delivery failure. This way the shipping risk will be truly minimized. The issues such as on route delay and other unexpected things may happen that we are willing to do our best to avoid and to help solving them if it happened. However, we are not able to take the responsibility on the import duties you may be charged by the custom.

